+ Process CDC with\nthe AUTO CDC API
++ AUTO CDC API
+++_ Part of Lakeflow Declarative Pipelines
+++_ Handles deduplication automatically
+++_ Manages out-of-order records
++ Key Parameters
+++_ target: destination streaming table
+++_ keys: primary key columns
+++_ sequence_by: ordering column
+++_ apply_as_deletes: delete condition
-- SCD Type 1
---_ Overwrites current row on update
---_ No history retained
---_ Seattle → Portland replaces record
-- SCD Type 2
---_ Preserves all versions
---_ __START_AT / __END_AT columns
---_ Full audit history available
@endmindmap
